</span><span class='line'><span class="l-Scalar-Plain">&lt;p&gt;description</span><span class="p-Indicator">:</span> <span class="l-Scalar-Plain">This is an example post.</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="l-Scalar-Plain">twitter_card:&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="l-Scalar-Plain">&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;type</span><span class="p-Indicator">:</span> <span class="l-Scalar-Plain">photo</span>
